content: अशून्य {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@--1@} Not empty or vacant; तस्य निन्यतुरशून्यतामुभे <ls>R. 19. 13</ls> occupied. {@--2@} Not unattended to, fulfilled, executed; स्वनियोगमशून्यं कुरु (occurring frequently in dramas), execute or go about your business. --न्यं {@--1@} Not a void. {@--2@} Something sent to accompany another; लेखस्याशून्यार्थं किंचिदनुप्रेषितं <ls>Mu. 5</ls>; अयं लेखस्याशून्यार्थो भविष्यति {%<ab>ibid.</ab>%} (an accompaniment such as a customary present accompanying a letter).
